      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he went to confer with his superior, and they both came back, and he said, OK, you can go, but if you come back, we have to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't mean anything, because by this time, you know, you sort of get numb.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got back into the train, and this couple that were taking me, they said, OK, now you crawl under the bench.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the European trains have compartments where three people sit on one side, three people on the other facing each other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there's a little door to the compartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
